@SIGO_HostAddress = http://localhost:5044
@AccessToken = paste-jwt-token-here

### Health liveness - anonymous
GET {{SIGO_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Health readiness - anonymous, checks database connectivity
GET {{SIGO_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### Login as cliente - anonymous
POST {{SIGO_HostAddress}}/api/clientes/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "cliente@example.com",
  "password": "change-me"
}

###

### Protected cliente lookup - requires JWT bearer token
GET {{SIGO_HostAddress}}/api/clientes/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}

###

### OpenAPI document - development environment only
GET {{SIGO_HostAddress}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json
